main event: A witness observed a silver or gray colored object in the sky for 15 to 30 seconds in DeLand, Florida.
interesting points: The object was described as having 'V' like a boomerang shape., The observation was made from a car window., The object moved in a straight and level flight from North to South., The local police and military reported no unusual activities during the sighting., The event took place on a clear night with no obstructions to visibility.
witness description: A young female student from Stetson University.
